>|> *eat* their one-time pad or whatnot.
>|> 
>|> So what I'm looking for from you folks is this:
>|> 
>|>        Where can I *get* some of this stuff?
>|> 
>|>        ...or how would I *make* something similar to it?


>Edible rice paper is a specialty item in Japanese cooking.
>I've seen it in various sizes, from 3"x3" to about a foot square.

>It is also used in some Western confectionary constructions.
>I wouldn't be surprised if it is used in other cooking as well.


